title: Person Of Interest Season 5 finale, John's Death | Part 1
author: ReWatch TV
comment: I cried when Reese went down............
Sometimes I watch this ending and I cry like every single time I watch this, definitly a great serie with deep characters...

There was a really good edit of this, where they cut to The Machine's simulation and the machine wins one. implying that all this is yet to happen and that it does in fact, not have to happen. Personally I thought that would have been far more clever.
It's so sad, but this is what he wanted.  It's majestic and a memorial.  Not all of us get out alive.
